    "en": {
      "title": "UN President meeting with representatives",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "A meeting between President Ranil Wickremesinghe and United Nations representatives took place yesterday (18) afternoon.",
        "The meeting held at the President's Office was attended by the Director of the Bangkok Office for Development Coordination for the Asia and Pacific Region, David Masnekyan Carr, the United Nations Permanent Representative, Hena Singer, and the Head of the United Nations Resident Coordinator's Office, Andreas Garbadi.",
        "The President's Director of International Affairs, Dinuk Kolambake, and the President's Director of Youth and Sustainable Development Affairs, Randula Abedira, also attended the meeting. (a)"
      ],
